&lt;p&gt;Applications are invited for a substantive Consultant post in Intensive Care at the CQC-rated ‘outstanding’ Bristol Royal Infirmary. Recent service expansion and integration means that our dynamic, committed and forward-thinking team now provides cutting-edge tertiary care to patients across 50 ICU beds. This exciting and progressive clinical environment is strengthened by advanced digital technology, wide-ranging research activities and major University teaching status. The successful applicant will thrive within a multi-disciplinary team that prides itself on delivering the highest quality of critical care.&lt;/p&gt;
